Dilithion Core Contributors
============================

This file lists the people who have contributed code, documentation, or
research to the Dilithion project. See the Acknowledgements section below
for the upstream projects Dilithion builds upon.

To add your name, open a pull request — contributions are welcome.

Core developers
---------------
